💍 VivahSetu – Wedding Planning & Vendor Management Platform

A secure and scalable Wedding Planning Management System built using Spring Boot, Spring Cloud, Microservices Architecture, Spring Data JPA, MySQL, Eureka Service Discovery, API Gateway, and JWT Authentication. The platform helps couples efficiently plan weddings, manage budgets, track tasks, book vendors, and manage wedding-related services through independent microservices.

🚀 Features

1. User Registration and Login with JWT Authentication
2. Microservices-Based Architecture
3. API Gateway for Centralized Routing
4. Eureka Service Discovery for Service Registration
5. Wedding Planning and Management
6. Vendor Registration and Approval System
7. Vendor Search by City and Category
8. Wedding Budget Tracking and Expense Management
9. Wedding Task Creation and Completion Tracking
10. Booking Management and Confirmation
11. Dashboard for Wedding Planning Insights
12. RESTful APIs with Layered Architecture
13. Exception Handling and Data Validation

